<tr id="L350"><td><a href="#L350">350</a></td><td>PICARD:  If you believe I am all-powerful, then you cannot hurt me. If, however, I am telling the truth and I am mortal, you will kill me. But if the only proof you will believe is my death, then shoot.</td></tr>

<tr id="L351"><td><a href="#L351">351</a></td><td>NURIA:  Liko, don't do it!</td></tr>

